---
import Foundation from '../../../assets/about/Pik17.jpg';
import growthExpansion from '../../../assets/about/Pik12.jpg';
import innovation from '../../../assets/about/Pik9.jpg';
---

<section class="relative py-16 md:py-20 px-4 overflow-hidden bg-background">

	<div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
		<div class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-accent/10 blur-[130px] rounded-full"></div>
		<div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-accent/10 blur-[130px] rounded-full"></div>
	</div>

	<div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto">

		<!-- Section Header -->
		<div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-14 md:mb-16">
			<p class="text-accent text-xs tracking-[0.3em] font-semibold uppercase mb-2">
				OUR JOURNEY
			</p>

			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">
				The Story Behind
				<span class="text-accent"> Avietho</span>
			</h2>

			<p class="text-text-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
				Since 2018, Avietho Digital Marketing has grown from a passionate
				creative team into a trusted digital marketing partner for businesses,
				government agencies, and political leaders across the Philippines.
			</p>
		</div>

		<!-- Timeline Content Container -->
		<div class="relative">

			<div class="hidden lg:block absolute left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-[2px] bg-accent/30 -translate-x-1/2"></div>

			<!-- Milestone 1: 2018 -->
			<div class="relative grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center mb-14 md:mb-16">

				<div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
					<div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-accent/20 bg-card h-[250px] md:h-[280px]">
						<img
							src={Foundation.src}
							alt="Foundation"
							class="w-full h-full object-cover"
							loading="lazy"
						/>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="order-1 lg:order-2 relative">
					<span class="text-accent text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider">
						2018
					</span>

					<h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-foreground mt-2 mb-3">
						Foundation
					</h3>

					<p class="text-text-subtle text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
						Avietho Digital Marketing was established in Muntinlupa City with
						a vision of helping businesses build stronger digital identities
						through creativity, strategy, and innovation. From the very
						beginning, the company focused on delivering measurable results
						and long-term partnerships.
					</p>
				</div>

			</div>

			<!-- Milestone 2: 2020 -->
			<div class="relative grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center mb-14 md:mb-16">

				<div>
					<span class="text-accent text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider">
						2020
					</span>

					<h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-foreground mt-2 mb-3">
						Growth & Expansion
					</h3>

					<p class="text-text-subtle text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
						As demand increased, Avietho expanded its expertise into political
						campaigns, multimedia production, branding, government projects,
						and integrated digital marketing solutions, becoming a full-service
						creative agency.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div>
					<div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-accent/20 bg-card h-[250px] md:h-[280px]">
						<img
							src={growthExpansion.src}
							alt="Growth & Expansion"
							class="w-full h-full object-cover"
							loading="lazy"
						/>
					</div>
				</div>

			</div>

			<!-- Milestone 3: 2023 -->
			<div class="relative grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center">

				<div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
					<div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-accent/20 bg-card h-[250px] md:h-[280px]">
						<img
							src={innovation.src}
							alt="Innovation"
							class="w-full h-full object-cover"
							loading="lazy"
						/>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="order-1 lg:order-2 relative">
					<span class="text-accent text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider">
						2023
					</span>

					<h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-foreground mt-2 mb-3">
						Innovation
					</h3>

					<p class="text-text-subtle text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
						Today, Avietho continues to innovate through web development,
						multimedia production, branding, digital campaigns, and
						data-driven marketing strategies that help organizations thrive
						in an ever-changing digital landscape.
					</p>
				</div>

			</div>

		</div>

	</div>

</section>